text: Shop had a good variety of malay food not normally found in most shops! Its has nasi padang, nasi sambal goreng, lontong, gado-gado and ayam penyet as well. On top of that, they sell porridges and kuehs too. Would definitely come back to try their other dishes.

You can find one of the nicest nasi sambal goreng, mee rebus, mee soto and laksa here! Nasi padang too, of course.
